%section.hero-splash{style: "background-image: url(#{image_path("backgrounds/circle.jpg")});"}
  .container
    .centered-row
      %h4.leader Learn to code
      %h1 Become a Developer
      %p.lead With the largest Career Support team of any UK bootcamp, we guarantee you a job offer within 6 months, or your money back. We're highly-selective about our Hiring Partners – no temp jobs or internships. Over 1,400 developers have started their careers with over 300 companies.
