%section
  .container
    .centered-row
      %h2 The fastest route
      %h4.subheader into the tech industry
      %p.lead Upskill and transition into a new career in 16 weeks.
    .three-width-row
      .column
        %h4.leader Average Salary
        %h2 £30-35k
        %p Over the past five years, our historic average starting salary is £32k. Makers developers typically earn above £40k one year later.
      .column
        %h4.leader Average Days Jobhunting
        %h2 40
        %p 1:1 Career Support coaching and frequent, well-attended Career Fairs get you introduced and accepted with the right company, fast.
      .column
        %h4.leader Hiring Partners
        %h2 300+
        %p We're incredibly selective about our Hiring Partners: progressive organisations at the cutting-edge of digital innovation.

%section.backgrounded{style: "background-image: url(#{image_path("backgrounds/circle-of-students.jpg")});"}
